M.Sc. Alyric Leeman 10/02/72Hello, these are the musing of Apollo Site Lab Technician, Alyric Leeman. I have been herefor one year and… I’ve expected more. Security screenings, a private flight and a helicopterride up north to this lab. I thought this was the “in” on groundbreaking research to helppeople. That is what they told me at least. I can’t contact loved ones, and they can’tcontact me… I miss my dog… I love you Cujo. I know I signed an NDA, but these noteswon’t leave the facility let alone storage so screw it. Better to pass the time this way thanlooking at boxes of gloves.
